<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Email Verification</title>
    <style>
        .container {
            font-family: sans-serif;
            padding: 20px;
            color: #333;
        }

        .button {
            background-color: #e44d26;
            color: white !important;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #888;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            padding-top: 10px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Welcome to ClothesShop!</h1>
        <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
        <p>Thank you for registering. Please verify your email address to activate your account and start shopping.</p>
        <a href="{{url}}" class="button">Verify Email Address</a>
        <p>If the button doesn't work, you can also click the link below:</p>
        <p><a href="{{url}}">{{url}}</a></p>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>This email was sent by ClothesShop. If you did not register for an account, please ignore this email.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>